  77,13,"f'idha alnujum tumst wadhahab dyawha, wa'iidha alsama' tsddaet, wa'iidha aljibal ttayrt wtnathrt wasarat haba'an tadhrwh alryah, wa'iidha alrusul euyin lahum waqt wa'ajal llfsl baynahum wabayn alamm, yqal: lay yawm eazim akhkhirt alrsl? akhkhirt liawm alqada' walfsl bayn alkhlayq. wama aelmk -ayha al'insan- ay shay' hu yawm alfasl wshdth whwlh? hlak eazim fi dhalik alyawm lilmukadhibin bhdha alyawm almwewd"
  77,14,"f'idha alnujum tumst wadhahab dyawha, wa'iidha alsama' tsddaet, wa'iidha aljibal ttayrt wtnathrt wasarat haba'an tadhrwh alryah, wa'iidha alrusul euyin lahum waqt wa'ajal llfsl baynahum wabayn alamm, yqal: lay yawm eazim akhkhirt alrsl? akhkhirt liawm alqada' walfsl bayn alkhlayq. wama aelmk -ayha al'insan- ay shay' hu yawm alfasl wshdth whwlh? hlak eazim fi dhalik alyawm lilmukadhibin bhdha alyawm almwewd"
  77,15,"f'idha alnujum tumst wadhahab dyawha, wa'iidha alsama' tsddaet, wa'iidha aljibal ttayrt wtnathrt wasarat haba'an tadhrwh alryah, wa'iidha alrusul euyin lahum waqt wa'ajal llfsl baynahum wabayn alamm, yqal: lay yawm eazim akhkhirt alrsl? akhkhirt liawm alqada' walfsl bayn alkhlayq. wama aelmk -ayha al'insan- ay shay' hu yawm alfasl wshdth whwlh? hlak eazim fi dhalik alyawm lilmukadhibin bhdha alyawm almwewd"
  77,16,"'alam nuhlik alssabiqin min al'umam almadyt; btkdhybhm lilrusul kqwm nuh waead wthmwd? thuma nlhq bihim almtakhryn mmn kanuu mathaluhum fi altkdhyb walesyan. mithl dhlk al'ihlak alfzye nafeal bhwla' almujrimin min kafaar \"mk\"; ltkdhybhm alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  77,17,"alm nuhlik alssabiqin min al'umam almadyt; btkdhybhm lilrusul kqwm nuh waead wthmwd? thuma nlhq bihim almtakhryn mmn kanuu mathaluhum fi altkdhyb walesyan. mithl dhlk al'ihlak alfzye nafeal bhwla' almujrimin min kafaar \"mk\"; ltkdhybhm alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  77,18,"alm nuhlik alssabiqin min al'umam almadyt; btkdhybhm lilrusul kqwm nuh waead wthmwd? thuma nlhq bihim almtakhryn mmn kanuu mathaluhum fi altkdhyb walesyan. mithl dhlk al'ihlak alfzye nafeal bhwla' almujrimin min kafaar \"mk\"; ltkdhybhm alrasul salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  77,19,"hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat likuli mkdhdhib bi'ana allah hu al'ilh alhaqu wahdah la sharik lh, walnbwt walbeth walhsab"
  77,20,"alm nkhlqkm- ya maeshar alkfar- min maa' daeif hqyr wahu alntft, fajaealna hdha alma' fi makan hsyn, wahu rahim almrat, 'iilaa waqt mahdud wmelwm eind allah teala? faqadarna ealaa khalaqah wtswyrh w'ikhrajh, faniem alqadirun nhn"
  77,21,"alm nkhlqkm- ya maeshar alkfar- min maa' daeif hqyr wahu alntft, fajaealna hdha alma' fi makan hsyn, wahu rahim almrat, 'iilaa waqt mahdud wmelwm eind allah teala? faqadarna ealaa khalaqah wtswyrh w'ikhrajh, faniem alqadirun nhn"
  77,22,"alm nkhlqkm- ya maeshar alkfar- min maa' daeif hqyr wahu alntft, fajaealna hdha alma' fi makan hsyn, wahu rahim almrat, 'iilaa waqt mahdud wmelwm eind allah teala? faqadarna ealaa khalaqah wtswyrh w'ikhrajh, faniem alqadirun nhn"
  77,23,"'alam nkhlqkm- ya maeshar alkfar- min maa' daeif hqyr wahu alntft, fajaealna hdha alma' fi makan hsyn, wahu rahim almrat, 'iilaa waqt mahdud wmelwm eind allah teala? faqadarna ealaa khalaqah wtswyrh w'ikhrajh, faniem alqadirun nhn"
  77,24,hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin bqdrtna
  77,25,"alm najeal hadhih al'ard alty teyshwn elyha, tadumu ealaa zahriha 'ahya' la yhswn, wafi btnha amwatana la yhsrwn, wajaealna fiha jbala thwabt ealyat; lialaa tdtrb bkm, wa'asqaynakum ma'an edhbana sayghana?"
  77,26,"alm najeal hadhih al'ard alty teyshwn elyha, tadumu ealaa zahriha 'ahya' la yhswn, wafi btnha amwatana la yhsrwn, wajaealna fiha jbala thwabt ealyat; lialaa tdtrb bkm, wa'asqaynakum ma'an edhbana sayghana?"
  77,27,"alm najeal hadhih al'ard alty teyshwn elyha, tadumu ealaa zahriha 'ahya' la yhswn, wafi btnha amwatana la yhsrwn, wajaealna fiha jbala thwabt ealyat; lialaa tdtrb bkm, wa'asqaynakum ma'an edhbana sayghana?"
  77,28,hlak wdmar yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin bhdhh alnem
  77,29,"yqal lilkafirin yawm alqyamt: siruu 'iilaa eadhab jahanam aladhi kuntum bih tukadhibun fi aldnya, syru, fastzlu bidukhan jahanam ytfre minh thlath qte, la yuzil dhlk alzili min hurun dhlk alyawm, wala yadfae min hurun allahab shyyana. 'iina jahanam tqdhf min alnaar bisharar ezym, kl shararat minh kalbna' almshyd fi aleizm walartfae. ka'an shrr jahanam almttayr minha 'ibl sud ymyl lawnuha 'iilaa alssufrt"
  77,30,"yqal lilkafirin yawm alqyamt: siruu 'iilaa eadhab jahanam aladhi kuntum bih tukadhibun fi aldnya, syru, fastzlu bidukhan jahanam ytfre minh thlath qte, la yuzil dhlk alzili min hurun dhlk alyawm, wala yadfae min hurun allahab shyyana. 'iina jahanam tqdhf min alnaar bisharar ezym, kl shararat minh kalbna' almshyd fi aleizm walartfae. ka'an shrr jahanam almttayr minha 'ibl sud ymyl lawnuha 'iilaa alssufrt"
  77,31,"yuqal lilkafirin yawm alqyamt: siruu 'iilaa eadhab jahanam aladhi kuntum bih tukadhibun fi aldnya, syru, fastzlu bidukhan jahanam ytfre minh thlath qte, la yuzil dhlk alzili min hurun dhlk alyawm, wala yadfae min hurun allahab shyyana. 'iina jahanam tqdhf min alnaar bisharar ezym, kl shararat minh kalbna' almshyd fi aleizm walartfae. ka'an shrr jahanam almttayr minha 'ibl sud ymyl lawnuha 'iilaa alssufrt"
  77,32,"yqal lilkafirin yawm alqyamt: siruu 'iilaa eadhab jahanam aladhi kuntum bih tukadhibun fi aldnya, syru, fastzlu bidukhan jahanam ytfre minh thlath qte, la yuzil dhlk alzili min hurun dhlk alyawm, wala yadfae min hurun allahab shyyana. 'iina jahanam tqdhf min alnaar bisharar ezym, kl shararat minh kalbna' almshyd fi aleizm walartfae. ka'an shrr jahanam almttayr minha 'ibl sud ymyl lawnuha 'iilaa alssufrt"
  77,33,"yqal lilkafirin yawm alqyamt: siruu 'iilaa eadhab jahanam aladhi kuntum bih tukadhibun fi aldnya, syru, fastzlu bidukhan jahanam ytfre minh thlath qte, la yuzil dhlk alzili min hurun dhlk alyawm, wala yadfae min hurun allahab shyyana. 'iina jahanam tqdhf min alnaar bisharar ezym, kl shararat minh kalbna' almshyd fi aleizm walartfae. ka'an shrr jahanam almttayr minha 'ibl sud ymyl lawnuha 'iilaa alssufrt"
  77,34,hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin bweyd allh
  77,35,"hdha yawm alqiamat aldhy la yantiq fih almukadhibun bklam ynfehm, wala yakun lahum 'iidhan fi alkalam fyetdhrwn; li'anah la edhr lhm"
  77,36,"hdha yawm alqiamat aldhy la yantiq fih almukadhibun bklam ynfehm, wala yakun lahum 'iidhan fi alkalam fyetdhrwn; li'anah la edhr lhm"
  77,37,hlak waeadhab shadid yawmayidh lilmukadhibin bhdha alyawm wama fyh
  77,38,"hadha yawm yafsil allah fih bayn alkhlayq, wytmyz fih alhaqu min albatl, jamaenakum fih -ya maeshar kafaar hadhih alamt- mae alkufaar al'awalin min al'umam almadyt, fa'iin kan lakum hilatan fi alkhalas min aleadhab fahtalu, wanqdhu 'anfusakum min batsh allah wantqamh"
  77,39,"hdha yawm yafsil allah fih bayn alkhlayq, wytmyz fih alhaqu min albatl, jamaenakum fih -ya maeshar kafaar hadhih alamt- mae alkufaar al'awalin min al'umam almadyt, fa'iin kan lakum hilatan fi alkhalas min aleadhab fahtalu, wanqdhu 'anfusakum min batsh allah wantqamh"
  77,40,hlak wdmar yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biawm alqyamt
  77,41,"'in aladhin khafuu rabihim fi aldnya, wataquu eadhabah bamtthal awamrh wajtnab nwahyh, hum yawm alqiamat fi zilal al'ashjar alwarft waeuyun alma' aljaryt, wafawakih kathirat mimaa tashtahih 'anfusahum ytnemwn. yuqal lhm: kuluu 'aklana ldhydhana, washrabuu shrbana hnyyana; bsbb ma qadamtum fi aldunya min salih alaemal. 'iinaa bimithl dhlk aljaza' aleazim najzi 'ahl al'iihsan fi 'aemalahum wtaethm lna. hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biawm aljaza' walhisab wama fih min alnaeim waledhab"
  77,42,"'in aladhin khafuu rabihim fi aldnya, wataquu eadhabah bamtthal awamrh wajtnab nwahyh, hum yawm alqiamat fi zilal al'ashjar alwarft waeuyun alma' aljaryt, wafawakih kathirat mimaa tashtahih 'anfusahum ytnemwn. yuqal lhm: kuluu 'aklana ldhydhana, washrabuu shrbana hnyyana; bsbb ma qadamtum fi aldunya min salih alaemal. 'iinaa bimithl dhlk aljaza' aleazim najzi 'ahl al'iihsan fi 'aemalahum wtaethm lna. hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biawm aljaza' walhisab wama fih min alnaeim waledhab"
  77,43,"'iina aladhin khafuu rabihim fi aldnya, wataquu eadhabah bamtthal awamrh wajtnab nwahyh, hum yawm alqiamat fi zilal al'ashjar alwarft waeuyun alma' aljaryt, wafawakih kathirat mimaa tashtahih 'anfusahum ytnemwn. yuqal lhm: kuluu 'aklana ldhydhana, washrabuu shrbana hnyyana; bsbb ma qadamtum fi aldunya min salih alaemal. 'iinaa bimithl dhlk aljaza' aleazim najzi 'ahl al'iihsan fi 'aemalahum wtaethm lna. hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biawm aljaza' walhisab wama fih min alnaeim waledhab"
